{"tid":2172651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸人講韓國瑜，話境外的政界人士，走去北大讀書肯定有古怪","createTime":"2020-08-24T18:16:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T22:17:23.000Z","uid":171506,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"114443a3e5d738d65bcebb157f3b266560e2bdfe","tid":2172651,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T18:16:18.000Z","msg":"我為什麼懷疑韓國瑜有問題呢？比如：他為什麼在北大上了好幾年學？這人如果在北大上好幾年學，就肯定就值得懷疑了，那地方不是一般人就能去的，尤其台灣人，又是政界的。別說你是一台灣政界的，就是大陸一個普通人，不考試你能去北大上博士嗎？他沒有那個資格，能去的不是花錢，就是有安排的。一個清華、一個北大，這都是政治之手插得最深的地方。"},{"pid":"4d6d5b1627b30bce6f61207ca63f1b3fc1866d7a","tid":2172651,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T18:17:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/7/15/n12258347.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F20%2F7%2F15%2Fn12258347.htm&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3SbsLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=53c3d825\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/7/15/n12258347.htm</a>"},{"pid":"98645836a3019bd3a24b89bb19fdd0efb2fd0e18","tid":2172651,"uid":251732,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T18:19:19.000Z","msg":"鄭松泰<br />\nover my dead body"},{"pid":"79fbbc1b16cfc468f3e06da06542e4e2b6d61ca7","tid":2172651,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T18:22:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">[exchange] 派咗清華去唔去好<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/548984\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/548984</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span>"},{"pid":"f9bf7f14849af9f28d2a456629ab94d4fdd2c4af","tid":2172651,"uid":171506,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T18:30:48.000Z","msg":"共匪重點大學，點會唔係收靚的地方？<br />\n<br />\n普通大陸人讀上去，可能反而無乜嘢，但香港人或台灣人特登走去大陸讀書，然後回原居地從政，咁可能好鬼下"},{"pid":"4800f588a1868a31cedae873713676f5536e8393","tid":2172651,"uid":87576,"like":0,"dislike":0,